Package lab5.system.commands

Class UpdateId

java.lang.Object
lab5.system.commands.UpdateId
All Implemented Interfaces:
Command
public class UpdateId extends Object implements Command
Command to update a SpaceMarine object in the collection based on its ID. This class implements the Command interface and provides functionality to replace an existing SpaceMarine with a new one that has the same ID.
